details.description: **** SAMPLE DATA **** MOVE IN READY! The "Sonoma" by Rodrock Homes is a reverse 1.5 story on a walkout lot backing to trees.  A beautiful homesite! The Great Room has huge windows to let in the sunshine with a view of many trees. The Kitchen has an oversized island with custom cabinets and access to a covered deck  The huge walk in pantry is tucked away with a full bath and bedroom behind the kitchen for privacy. Hang your coats at the drop zone off the garage door.  You will enjoy the view out the dining room windows next to kitchen that leads to the covered deck. The Primary bedroom suite has a private entry with an en suite bath that provides  dual vanities, shower and an enormous walk-in closet. The lower has a Recreation Room with a walk up bar and 2 more bedrooms and bath.  So many trees for afternoon- evening shade on the patio as this home faces west.  Stonebridge Trails is a Rodrock Community. Wonderful amenities with 2 clubhouses, 1 with work out facility, 4 pools, playgrounds, basketball and tennis courts and nature trails through out the neighborhood. Close to Heritage Park that provides a dog park, golfing, picnic areas and more! Taxes, square footage, and room dimensions are estimated. Buyer Agent or Buyer to verify. **** SAMPLE DATA ****
details.extras: Cooktop, Dishwasher, Disposal, Exhaust Fan, Humidifier, Microwave, Built-In Oven
